Proud of seeing @zaz.brw surrounded by so many people interested in tapping into her wisdom. She is a force of nature making hard conversations happen. You can‚Äôt spend a day next to her without learning something new. 
As a man, I can‚Äôt stay blind to the privilege I luckily inherited: women face continuous challenges and injustices that we, as men, ignore (or worse, perpetuate). While the topic is by nature full of nuances and different opinions, the universal truth is that their body is their body. From abortion to contraception, from FGM to motherhood-as-a-destiny, this simple universal rule is too often forgotten. 
Dear men, whatever is your opinion, listen to women. Their experience will guide you.
